{"tid":1372684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現場人士可唔可以再敲打欄杆路牌？","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:52:24.000Z","uid":16483,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b36a55e9b4ef3a5dd465af1de3349527f00ff89","tid":1372684,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:22:40.000Z","msg":"今日發夢都朗屏站對出麗新個到對犬隻對待，但現場資訊傳得非常慢，邊到有防暴有速龍唔知，講緊幾點散又傳傳下無左聲氣，有白車有物資要讓路又聽唔到。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話敲打啲野振奮士氣唔好，但都唔係由頭敲到落尾都無撚停過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩下次咁多位適可而止，間竭性咁敲，唔好連放左催淚彈都係到敲，根本聽唔到啲人係想退定上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826f197361edac74bcf4d915f91ca073e99ffd0d","tid":1372684,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b523c0a64d78764dd4ef10470b812b40ac799d2","tid":1372684,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"或者我唔知敲野可能有其他功用，求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94083be041ffd27b6c5db60dd77ab57f6b1e0378","tid":1372684,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59939a509c4b6cb60f1b9e38dde489c295050dc5","tid":1372684,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"我真係唔知係咪有其他意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ecdab7e5b99d269ba30d646d002c3263fa5583","tid":1372684,"uid":215794,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"好煩<br />\n唔好連續敲咁耐<br />\n<br />\n這是無差別攻擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括對上面民居<br />\n對自己人"},{"pid":"7d1441024fa509cb176df1c639eb774d29203865","tid":1372684,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:5